Text:
Thank you for the great torrent, all episodes are good quality, but according to TV.com you are missing the following episodes:

Season 14 - Episode 12
Season 9 - Episodes 14 & 15
Season 4 - Episode 14

Season 3 has 14 episodes in the torrent but TV.com only has it at 13 episodes, so maybe episode 14 goes with season 4.

For those of you who are going to download this, in season 2 the last episode comes first, and they announce the winner in the first 30 seconds. So read the titles carefully before you watch if you don't want spoilers. Good torrent though, thanks for the upload!

Hi! Great download. PLEASE keep seeding everyone. It's taking forever and I have uncapped bandwidth and a really good PC...
